Features Easy configurations: Make a Discord bot easy and fast with a simple control panel. Add chat commands: You can always add new commands in few seconds. Pre-installed plugins: You don't have to download plugins. All released plugins are always included in the software. Export to Windows and Ubuntu: Export your bot, change the code and have fun.
